                  "value":"CONTROL: \"Good day Uniform-Alpha-Seven-Four-Niner, climb flight level three-seven-zero.\"\nAMANDA: \"Control, roger climb flight level three-seven-zero.\"\n\nCONTROL: \"Uniform-Alpha-Seven-Four-Niner, you're good for now.\"\nAMANDA: \"Control, roger that good for now. Thank you. Out.\"\n\n(click)\nDERRICK: \"Autopilot on and we're good. Hey Amanda, I will use the washroom.\"\nAMANDA: \"Sure.\"\n(cockpit door creak)\n\n(lock snap)\n(silence)\nAMANDA: (weeps)\nAMANDA: \"Sorry... I'm so sorry...\"\n(engine whirl)\n\n(door knock)\nDERRICK: \"Amanda, hey Amanda! What are you doing! Open the door!\"\n(rapid door knocks)\nDERRICK: \"AMANDA!\"\n\n(tumble)\n\n(alert bleep)\nMACHINE: \"TERRAIN. PULL-UP.\"\nMACHINE: \"TERRAIN, PULL-UP.\"\nAMANDA: (weeps and sniffs) \"Goodbye, love.\"\n(crash)\n\n(silence)\n\n"
