                  "value":"one passenger Hugo Dewitt broke the cabin windows and caused severe depressurisation, which compromised the hull integrity of the plane and eventually leading to the crash.\"\n\nRADIO: \"Investigation found that Mr Dewitt has purchased $1.1 million worth of life insurance with proceeds entitled to his disabled wife, Mrs Martha Dewitt. Mrs Dewitt was crippled from a previous crash landing of a flight UA125...\"\n\n"
